attributes.title: We're Here Together
attributes.caption: We've made it! Sunday has arrived, now let's get ready for the coming week with some chill vibes!

attributes.title: Learning to Breathe
attributes.description: It's another Sunday and we've all finally made it!

attributes.title: Passion From Chaos
attributes.caption: Kdin takes us through the ways to be be courageous and passionate and about how nostalgia can be key in finding happiness when things are uncertain.
attributes.description: Kdin takes us through the ways to be be courageous and passionate and about how nostalgia can be key in finding happiness when things are uncertain.

attributes.title: Staying Positive In Negativity
attributes.caption: Times are tough, but we're all much tougher! Kdin talks us through dealing with stress and learning to find ways to relax!
attributes.description: Times are tough, but we're all much tougher! Kdin talks us through dealing with stress and learning to find ways to relax!

attributes.title: Community Is Family
attributes.caption: Family can be weird, but it can also be whomever you feel closest to! And for a lot of us, that's THIS community!

attributes.title: Learning To Forgive
attributes.caption: Forgiveness can be difficult, especially for those really big issues, but finding ways to forgive someone or even yourself for those smaller problems can be the best way to paving a healthy path forward.
attributes.description: Forgiveness can be difficult, especially for those really big issues, but finding ways to forgive someone or even yourself for those smaller problems can be the best way to paving a healthy path forward.

attributes.title: Let's Talk About Mental Health!
attributes.caption: It's time to breath through that stigma and actually talk about your mental health, reach out for help, and realize you are STRONGER THAN YOU THINK!
